OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776694271
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police dog
OL,4,Cfinds cocaine stuffed steering wheel
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been jailed after a
OL,7,Fpolice dog uncovered cocaine inside
OL,8,Fhis steering wheel.
OL,10,FAngel Yankov was stopped on the A272
OL,11,Fnear Cowfold in March, after the
OL,12,FPeugeot 207 he was driving was linked
OL,13,Fto the supply of drugs.
OL,15,FOfficers initially found a small
OL,16,Famount of cannabis in the drivers'
OL,17,Fdoor, but decided to draft in police
OL,18,Fdog Jake, to do a more thorough search.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
