OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776694271
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police dog
OL,4,Cfinds cocaine stuffed steering wheel
OL,6,FSussex Police says PD Jake immediately
OL,7,Fnoticed something was up with the
OL,8,Fsteering wheel, and indicated to
OL,9,Fofficers that it was worth
OL,10,Finvestigating.
OL,12,FPolice then noticed that the wheel was
OL,13,F'soft' and the horn did not work. The
OL,14,Fcentrepiece was removed which revealed
OL,15,Fa sock containing more cannabis,
OL,16,Fseveral grip seal bags of cocaine and
OL,17,Fa quantity of cash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
