OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776694271
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after police dog
OL,4,Cfinds cocaine stuffed steering wheel
OL,6,FThe centrepiece was removed and a sock
OL,7,Fcontaining more cannabis, several grip
OL,8,Fseal bags of cocaine and a quantity of
OL,9,Fcash was discovered
OL,11,FYankov, aged 32, of no fixed address
OL,12,Fwas arrested and charged with
OL,13,Fpossession with intent to supply
OL,14,Fcocaine and cannabis.
OL,16,FHe appeared before Lewes Crown Court
OL,17,Fon 9 April, where he was sentenced to
OL,18,F20 months' imprisonment. He was also
OL,19,Fdisqualified from driving for 14
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
